metadata.name: St. Jerome
metadata.description:
A composite of Leonardo’s St. Jerome using three JPGs found on Google Images. This image is protected under fair use copyright law in the United States, as the original source imagery is transformed for a specific artistic purpose, i.e. to compile multiple found digital representations of a canonical artwork into a new single piece.
